name: Bitcoin Latinum
description: Bitcoin Latinum is the next generation, insured asset-backed cryptocurrency. Based on the Bitcoin ecosystem, Bitcoin Latinum is greener, faster and more secure, poised to revolutionize digital transactions. Built by a team of industry experts, it can manage massive transaction volume and enable the management of digital assets while being highly efficient. It plans to disrupt high growth industries such as Media, Gaming, Telecommunications and Cloud Computing.
